<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Suspicious Activity Alert</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7fc;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 25px;
            background-color: white;
            position: relative;
            animation: slideIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        .alert-box {
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ff4d4f;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
        }

        .alert-box h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .alert-box p {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ff4d4f;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1em;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #e60000;
        }

        .loader {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border: 6px solid #fff;
            border-top: 6px solid #ff4d4f;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            visibility: hidden;
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            0% { transform: translateY(-100%); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        /* Media Queries for Responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                width: 90%;
                padding: 15px;
            }

            .alert-box {
                padding: 20px;
                font-size: 1.1em;
            }

            .button {
                padding: 10px 18px;
                font-size: 0.95em;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .alert-box {
                font-size: 1em;
            }

            .button {
                padding: 10px 16px;
                font-size: 0.9em;
            }

            .loader {
                width: 30px;
                height: 30px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="alert-box">
            <h2>⚠️ Suspicious Activity Detected!</h2>
            <p>Your IP address has been flagged for potential malicious activity. Our security system has detected unusual patterns from your IP.</p>
            <p><strong>Action Required:</strong> Please Don't Try Again This Kind Of Activity</p>
            <a href="/" class="button" onclick="showLoader()">Go Back</a>
        </div>
        <div class="loader" id="loader"></div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showLoader() {
            document.getElementById('loader').style.visibility = 'visible';
            setTimeout(function() {
                window.location.href = '/';
            }, 2000);
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>
